sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant API Gateway
    participant Lambda Relayer
    participant SecretsMgr as AWS Secrets Manager
    participant Blockchain

    User->>Frontend: Initiate gasless action
    Frontend->>Frontend: Create & format transaction
    Frontend->>Frontend: Sign typed data (EIP-712)
    Frontend->>API Gateway: POST /relay (signed tx + signature)
    API Gateway->>Lambda Relayer: Forward request
    Lambda Relayer->>SecretsMgr: Get forwarder wallet
    Lambda Relayer->>Blockchain: Verify signature
    Lambda Relayer->>Blockchain: Submit transaction
    Blockchain-->>Lambda Relayer: Tx receipt
    Lambda Relayer-->>Frontend: Response
    Frontend-->>User: Update UI
